list.text: Shitty WIP port of super mario bros. To play it, click anywhere on the empty parts of the graph and hit Shift+Tab. The blue dot on at (0, 50) should get highlighted. When that happens, use the left-right arrow keys to start/stop moving and up arrow key to jump.
If the Shift+Tab thing doesn't work, you can also try Ctrl+Alt+p and then hit tab and see if the blue dot gets highlighted.
